@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Queens" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed.

                             How to play?

  The game is based on the type of move a Queen is allowed to do on 
a chess board (The Queen can move in 8 directions, horizontally, 
vertically and diagonally). You have to place 8 Queens in such a
way that none of them are in line with another.

  You play by clicking on an empty space where you want to place
a Queen, and a queen-like icon will appear there. If there are
other Queens in line, they will be removed from the board...

  A display, on the lower right in the window, shows how many
Queens are placed on the board as well as the actual total to place.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS:

  You can change the Queen icons colour, simply by clicking on any
Queen that are shown on the game board.

  You can restart the game any time by clicikg on the 'New Game'
button or with the Right-Amiga and "N" keys combination.

